{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act31side", "eventName": "懷黍離", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "HS-9", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "得果", "storyInfo": "績所做的一切，只為織就一幅“山河百景圖”。而這個計劃的根由，還要從一千年前算起。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g11_yumendesert", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "原來那些渺小生靈眼中的天地，是這副模樣。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "從那片混沌蒙昧中脫身走出，初次行走在蒼茫大地上。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我從何而來，往何處去？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "保留著那副龐大身軀的記憶，還有一些神乎其神的能力，以及有別於眼前芸芸眾生的壽命。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但也只得像懵懂孩童，跟著眼前眾人，有樣學樣。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "歲月漫長，我遇到過兩位老師。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在炎國的北邊，有一片荒地。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和那裡的人們正試著開墾農田。看著一棵棵莊稼從地裡長出來，也是十分有趣。不知道該去哪，要不要來這裡幫幫我的忙？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "那裡是什麼樣的地方？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……比起這些城鎮要荒涼許多，再加上還有一些東西從那扇門裡跑出來，有點危險。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過你要是想知道，“人”是什麼樣的，那裡說不定是個不錯的地方。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時間還長，可以慢慢找答案。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snow_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我第一次知道，原來生命間還有“同胞”這樣的概念。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "或許這就是他們能戰勝那些龐然大物的原因？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#12$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是稀奇，昨晚冰雹下那麼大，這些莊稼看起來竟然一點事都沒有。", "name": "辛勞的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#12$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許是運氣好呢？老天看大家種地辛苦，發了點善心呢？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "績，是你做的吧？", "name": "辛勞的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#12$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#6$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是覺得，大家辛辛苦苦工作半年，就因為這一場冰雹毀於一旦，實在是可惜……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "世間萬物都有自己的運行規律，一季莊稼毀了，埋在地裡，還能化作土地的肥料，來年的莊稼可以長得更好。", "name": "辛勞的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#12$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你救得了這片地的這一季莊稼，可炎國有多少片這樣的農田，有多少靠天吃飯的人。", "name": "辛勞的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#12$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是好心，但人們總要靠自己研究出在這片土地上找活路的辦法……", "name": "辛勞的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#12$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一天，您也會離去嗎？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "辛勞的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#12$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這片土地會永遠存在，生命將永遠存在。", "name": "辛勞的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#12$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_mini01_villagevacancy", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "天地萬物，都有各自的位置。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "可是我們生於天地間，如無根之木，無水之萍。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "無因無果，無始無終。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我們又該歸於何處？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "時過境遷。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tech_intro", "key": "$tech_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是來收糧食的商人？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今年各地大旱，聽說北邊這裡的糧倉還有餘裕。我來進點糧食，賣到糧食更緊張的地方去。", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天地不仁風雨不調，實在是苦了這些農民。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#8$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是荒年，對農民來說未必不是好事。", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生莫不是在說夢話，荒年對農民來說怎麼會是好事？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多簡單的道理，越是荒年，糧食越貴。", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每斤糧食賺一文，賣五百斤，和每斤糧食賺十文，賣一百斤。這筆帳三歲小孩都算得清楚。", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從小就生活在這，只知道糧食是用來餵飽百姓，救人性命的。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "外面的天地，竟還有這樣的道理。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你又沒見過大荒城外的世面，並非人人都是臨淵忘水的神人，只是守著這幾畝田地，哪能悟出天下那麼多道理。", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小伙子，我的商隊剛好缺一個管事，你有沒有興趣，跟我一起去走走？", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g04_yaninn", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "住店。", "name": "茶葉商販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老規矩，貨存倉庫，先結帳，再住店。", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這兩年尚蜀開出來不少茶田，您說要來做茶葉生意。怎麼只是在這包下了這一片客棧？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一車最上品的“蜀山青”，從這裡運到百灶，能賺多少錢，朝廷抽幾成稅？", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一路上要是平安順利，能有兩成毛利——已經是相當好做的買賣。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是這來來往往，不願意老實納稅的茶商都要從這條小路上走，我又能抽多少錢？", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣看來，還是您做的這筆買賣划算……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我分明看到，您扣過一些貨物交給了官府？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就是另一筆生意了。", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在官府工作的人，也是要交差的。", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您做這個生意，既不怕官府找麻煩，也不怕這些茶商捅刀子？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那樣對他們來說都不是划算買賣。", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是沒了我，茶商要嘛老老實實繳納稅款，要嘛冒著風險再找運貨的路。", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是沒了我，官府重新網羅這些走私販的消息得花多少錢；再或者，官逼商反，平叛又要花多少錢？", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三贏的買賣，的確是難得的划算生意。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在尚蜀待了有段時間了，這裡的菜色差不多吃膩了。把這邊的生意交給別人打理，我們再往東邊走走吧。", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去東邊，做什麼生意？礦產，漕運？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼生意賺錢，就做什麼生意……這一次，主要還是想回家看看。", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你之前不是問我，有沒有一句放之四海而皆準的道理？", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天下熙熙，皆為利來；天下攘攘，皆為利往。", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "法理道德，信仰名譽，世上沒有不能寫在帳本上的東西。", "name": "精明的商人"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……受教了。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#2$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "所見皆如此。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我好像，有點明白了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐，我算了一筆帳。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多年來，我們兄弟姐妹活在這炎國，各自的帳本上，盈虧如何。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大哥找到了自己的道，但始終不容於世，於人間愛不得、恨不得、糾纏不得，是虧。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "令姐逍遙自在，這片天地困不住她，自得其樂，是盈。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有幾個妹妹，不見得通透，倒也沒什麼煩惱，不盈不虧。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於二哥……總之，頡死了，無論如何，都是大虧。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們一家和炎國人打了一千年的交道，任由他們差遣，這筆帳，我實在算不出我們有半點好處。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……最重要的，是你，姐姐。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你當真是半點都不曾把利益得失放在心上？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$act16_loop", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "取而代之？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#6$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "望"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了復仇，也為我們，賭一個結局。", "name": "望"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……怎麼能做到？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#6$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十二分之一，怎麼能贏過整體？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#6$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這件事成敗幾何……你又有多少把握？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我算過很久……", "name": "望"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "棋盤縱橫十九道，棋路算盡……執黑先行者貼七目半，無半分可勝之機。", "name": "望"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只靠我一人，確實很難做到。", "name": "望"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以需要一些你的幫助。", "name": "望"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若是我告訴你，如果還有那唯一一點可能，唯有此路。", "name": "望"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你願不願意，賭上全部身家性命？", "name": "望"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g16_beautifulland", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你追得很緊。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生對自己當下所作所為或許得有個解釋。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "左公子想要怎樣的解釋？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "挑動邪魔危害百姓，篡奪國家工事，還有，謀害其他代理人生命。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的所作所為，罪責比起望猶有過之。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然對這些罪狀我還有些異議，不過，左公子現在想要怎麼做？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "交出那匹布，在司歲台的監視下回到京城。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按你說的做，我會得到什麼？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個聽候判決的機會。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜，這個價格我不太想接受。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是要與炎國為敵？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算如此，左公子又能做到什麼？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_swordexsheath"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bldwhoosh", "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "左樂上前一步，拔出了刀。"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欺負普通人，有意思嗎？", "name": "年"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$sheildimpact"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們——？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"i